!                                                                             !
! Z280 ASSEMBER OPERATION LABELS                                              !
!                                                                             !
! Defines the operator labels used in the z80 assembler, both machine codes   !
! and pseudo operators.                                                       !
! Use the following command to convert this file:                             !
!                                                                             !
!    hashtab                                                                  !
!                                                                             !
! The resulting file, opz280.res, will contain an opcode type definition,     !
! to be merged into mdz80.pas, and a resym table initalizer, to be placed     !
! in utz280.pas.                                                              !
! You also need to take the last value of opcode, and place this in the       !
! hash call at fndres in utz280.pas.                                          !
!                                                                             !
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

